INFO:
When you fetch this project from Git the first time, make sure to
1. install the ffmpeg tools
- powershell -> "winget install ffmpeg"
- locate the ffmpeg.exe, ffplay.exe and ffprobe.exe on your device
- copy or move these files in the lib directory

2. install the yt-dlp.exe
- powershell -> "winget install yt-dlp" (or manually in the web)
- locate the yt-dlp.exe file on your device and copy or move it to the lib directory

3. set the apikey in the properties (only necessary if you want to use the UI)
- use the google developer console to fetch the api key to use for this project

NOTE:
Currently, these files cannot be pushed to git, due to community git without the large filesystem
only allows pushing files with max. 20MB size!
Also: Never push the API key from the properties file!